      <title>markdown 常用语法总结</title>
      <link href="/2019/10/14/Hello-Hexo/"/>
      <url>/2019/10/14/Hello-Hexo/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>对于markdown的我还是秉承它的宗旨：简洁易读</p><h2 id="文本处理"><a href="#文本处理" class="headerlink" title="文本处理"></a>文本处理</h2><h3 id="1、字体"><a href="#1、字体" class="headerlink" title="1、字体"></a>1、字体</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;font face=&quot;黑体&quot;&gt;我是黑体字&lt;/font&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;font color=red&gt;我是红色&lt;/font&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;font size=5&gt;我是尺寸&lt;/font&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;font face=&quot;黑体&quot; color=green size=5&gt;我是黑体，绿色，尺寸为5&lt;/font&gt;</span><br><span class="line"># H1</span><br><span class="line">## H2</span><br><span class="line">### H3</span><br><span class="line">#### H4</span><br><span class="line">##### H5</span><br><span class="line">###### H6</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果如下：</p><ul><li><font face="黑体">我是黑体字</font></li><li><font color="red">我是红色</font></li><li><font size="5">我是尺寸</font></li><li><font face="黑体" color="green" size="5">我是黑体，绿色，尺寸为5</font></li><li><h1 id="H1"><a href="#H1" class="headerlink" title="H1"></a>H1</h1></li><li><h2 id="H2"><a href="#H2" class="headerlink" title="H2"></a>H2</h2></li><li><h3 id="H3"><a href="#H3" class="headerlink" title="H3"></a>H3</h3></li><li><h4 id="H4"><a href="#H4" class="headerlink" title="H4"></a>H4</h4></li><li><h5 id="H5"><a href="#H5" class="headerlink" title="H5"></a>H5</h5></li><li><h6 id="H6"><a href="#H6" class="headerlink" title="H6"></a>H6</h6></li></ul><h3 id="2、加粗，倾斜，删除线"><a href="#2、加粗，倾斜，删除线" class="headerlink" title="2、加粗，倾斜，删除线"></a>2、加粗，倾斜，删除线</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">*斜体*          _斜体_</span><br><span class="line">**粗体**        __粗体__</span><br><span class="line">***粗斜体***    ___粗斜体___</span><br><span class="line">~~删除线~~</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果如下：</p><ul><li><em>斜体</em>          <em>斜体</em></li><li><strong>粗体</strong>        <strong>粗体</strong></li><li><strong><em>粗斜体</em></strong>    <strong><em>粗斜体</em></strong></li><li><del>删除线</del></li></ul><h2 id="代码区"><a href="#代码区" class="headerlink" title="代码区"></a>代码区</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">三个反单引号开始与结束，组成代码区块。一个反单引号开始与结尾，组成单行代码区块。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>    多行代码区块    多行代码区块    多行代码区块<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">`单行代码块`</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></code></pre><p>效果如下：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">多行代码区块</span><br><span class="line">多行代码区块</span><br><span class="line">多行代码区块</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>`单行代码块      `</code></pre><h2 id="分隔线"><a href="#分隔线" class="headerlink" title="分隔线"></a>分隔线</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">三个-与三个* 都行。</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">***</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="效果如下："><a href="#效果如下：" class="headerlink" title="效果如下："></a>效果如下：</h2><hr><h2 id="超链接"><a href="#超链接" class="headerlink" title="超链接"></a>超链接</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[百度](http://baidu.com)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果如下：</p><ul><li><a href="http://baidu.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">百度</a> </li></ul><h2 id="插入图片"><a href="#插入图片" class="headerlink" title="插入图片"></a>插入图片</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">设置大小居中</span><br><span class="line">&lt;div align=center&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://pic27.nipic.com/20130320/8092962_210424307317_2.jpg&quot; width=&quot;100&quot; height=&quot;100&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">直接插入图片</span><br><span class="line">![百度](http://pic27.nipic.com/20130320/8092962_210424307317_2.jpg)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果如下：<br>    <div align="center"><img src="http://pic27.nipic.com/20130320/8092962_210424307317_2.jpg" width="100" height="100"></div><br>    <img src="http://pic27.nipic.com/20130320/8092962_210424307317_2.jpg" alt="百度"> </p><h2 id="表格"><a href="#表格" class="headerlink" title="表格"></a>表格</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">| 左对齐    |  右对齐 | 居中 |</span><br><span class="line">| :-------- | -------:| :--: |</span><br><span class="line">| Computer  | 5000 元 |  1台两台 |</span><br><span class="line">| Phone     | 19 元 |  1部 |</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果如下：</p><table><thead><tr><th align="left">左对齐</th><th align="right">右对齐</th><th align="center">居中</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="left">Computer</td><td align="right">5000 元</td><td align="center">1台两台</td></tr><tr><td align="left">Phone</td><td align="right">19 元</td><td align="center">1部</td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="流程图"><a href="#流程图" class="headerlink" title="流程图"></a>流程图</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">st=&gt;start: 开始</span><br><span class="line">e=&gt;end: 结束</span><br><span class="line">op=&gt;operation: 我的操作</span><br><span class="line">cond=&gt;condition: 确认？</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">st-&gt;op-&gt;cond</span><br><span class="line">cond(yes)-&gt;e</span><br><span class="line">cond(no)-&gt;op</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果如下：</p><p>st=&gt;start: 开始<br>e=&gt;end: 结束<br>op=&gt;operation: 我的操作<br>cond=&gt;condition: 确认？</p><p>st-&gt;op-&gt;cond<br>cond(yes)-&gt;e<br>cond(no)-&gt;op</p>]]></content>
      
      
